{"tid":1957242,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"求醫好過疲勞至冇法返工/學嘅中醫","createTime":"2020-04-03T18:01:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-11T09:41:56.000Z","uid":46752,"like":1,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c8c2445a96976f4511025367dbf7bb315af3a45c","tid":1957242,"uid":46752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T18:01:32.000Z","msg":"主訴：<br />\n累，不夠體力自理（煮飯），職業治療師診斷我手做重複性動作會累<br />\n如以炸雞薯條作正餐，怕大便會全爛<br />\n<br />\n現史：<br />\n如吃粗糧，肚臍上9cm位置會頂<br />\n怕吃冷食物<br />\n手腳掌出汗，手腳掌冰冷<br />\n小便分差，陽痿（連皮/剝皮香蕉硬度）<br />\n<br />\n往史:<br />\n5-8年前，曾經常吃龜苓膏、飲涼茶<br />\n以前有手淫習慣<br />\n12年9月開始疲倦至今<br />\n14年5月開始嚴重地病，停學3年<br />\n<br />\n西醫:<br />\n腦神經內科做了神經傳導檢查，冇mri腦睇吓係咪多發性硬化症。<br />\n內分泌科排除了Cushing's syndrome。<br />\n叫咗醫生轉介咗我去精神科。<br />\n照過胸背x光。<br />\n有脂肪肝。<br />\n14年驗出肝酵素高。<br />\n17年照胃鏡，有胃炎。 脂肪肝。<br />\n<br />\n舊中醫處方<a href=\"https://photos.app.goo.gl/9MZZuLHDzs1esvbA6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphotos.app.goo.gl%2F9MZZuLHDzs1esvbA6&d=dfx5yx0%2Fy135WOof7TdQygUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=4dd2be39\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://photos.app.goo.gl/9MZZuLHDzs1esvbA6</a><br />\n<br />\ntg:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/Usernamennn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FUsernamennn&d=dfx5yx0%2Fy135WOof7TdQygUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=bdbbfbd3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Usernamennn</a><br />\nfb messager:<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.me/seek.chinesemedicine.1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.me%2Fseek.chinesemedicine.1&d=dfx5yx0%2Fy135WOof7TdQygUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=5a1f681e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.me/seek.chinesemedicine.1</a><br />\ntg gp:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/E38pyFcoqheNbzSaruFL-Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FE38pyFcoqheNbzSaruFL-Q&d=dfx5yx0%2Fy135WOof7TdQygUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=5906158e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/E38pyFcoqheNbzSaruFL-Q</a><br />\n<br />\n請問<br />\n1佢醫好過疲勞（冇法返工/學）？<br />\n2佢有咩成功重症經驗<br />\n3介唔介意分享你咩病<br />\n4你睇咗幾個、幾耐中醫？"},{"pid":"6234faed3c7f302c92bf6d01ae195587b632fc1d","tid":1957242,"uid":167548,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T18:12:11.000Z","msg":"飲涼茶飲到虧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08e22534a8c649fe8b75ab1adcaf8660af093126","tid":1957242,"uid":46752,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6234faed3c7f302c92bf6d01ae195587b632fc1d","tid":1957242,"uid":167548,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T18:12:11.000Z","msg":"飲涼茶飲到虧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T18:15:45.000Z","msg":"落井下石<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48e933e109579d44a083b4168cc3bb3b759d9bc2","tid":1957242,"uid":237487,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T18:40:13.000Z","msg":"又係你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你似心理有問題多過生理呀巴打"},{"pid":"d9439b3d11c0d30c49f6aadaffd9f708a06c34a2","tid":1957242,"uid":46752,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"48e933e109579d44a083b4168cc3bb3b759d9bc2","tid":1957242,"uid":237487,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T18:40:13.000Z","msg":"又係你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你似心理有問題多過生理呀巴打"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T18:40:42.000Z","msg":"我兩樣都會睇哂"},{"pid":"fecf92c26dbe1e67f2d74769ce6a0dab354b34e0","tid":1957242,"uid":51698,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T18:42:11.000Z","msg":"Chronic fatigue syndrome?<br />\n利申唔識醫學"},{"pid":"ff35072d44aefd22b1028286c8f10a2a8b5ec35a","tid":1957242,"uid":237487,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"d9439b3d11c0d30c49f6aadaffd9f708a06c34a2","tid":1957242,"uid":46752,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"48e933e109579d44